    {
      "description": "This Contract for Ending the Silence (ETS) to educate middle and high school aged young people to identify mental health conditions affecting themselves and/or their peers and approach these conditions in a compassionate and stigma-free manner is hereby amended to extend the term, increase funds, update the scope of work, and add clauses to the Contract."
